stake.t.sol
├── given staking is paused
│   └── it should revert
└── given staking is unpaused
    └── given the staking allowlist is true
        ├── when the caller is not a permissioned node
        │   └── it should revert
        └── when the caller is a permissioned node OR staking allowlist is off
            ├── when the amount to stake is lt the min stake
            │   └── it should revert
            └── when the amount to stake is gte the min stake
                ├── given the caller has not approved the amount to stake
                │   └── it should revert
                └── given the caller has approved the amount to stake
                    ├── given the caller does not have enough balance
                    │   └── it should revert
                    └── given the caller has enough balance
                        ├── it should increase the total staked for the caller
                        ├── it should transfer the amount of tokens to stake from the caller to the contract
                        └── it should emit a {Staked} event
